news/tv/phoebe-waller-bridge-to-write-tomb-raider-series-for-prime-video-3756342">合作开发新的<em>《古墓丽影》</em>系列</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-waller-bridge">菲比·沃勒-布里奇</a>将担任该剧的编剧和监制。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/heres-when-netflix-animated-tomb-raider-series-is-coming-out-3761818">Netflix 动画《古墓丽影》系列即将上映的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
